BUTTONS

 - Engine / World Operations

   F1            : fullscreen
                   (leaks mem, old crufty X code needs replacement)

   F2            : fps toggle
                   (console)

   F3            : decrease Minimum Critters
   F4            : increase Minimum Critters

   F7            : insert Adam
                   alternatively this can be used as a population reduction mechanism,
                   by inserting a considering amount of adams, the current population size
                   will drop.

   F11           : load all critters from "~/.critterding/load" directory
   F12           : save all critters into "~/.critterding/save/(timestamp)" directory

   Insert        : toggle critter vision

   w             : create a horizontal wall
   x             : destroy the wall
   c             : toggle gate in wall center

   f             : toggle follow the youngest critter untill it dies.

   Page Up       : increase energy in the system by the energy amount of 1 food
   Page Down     : decrease energy in the system by the energy amount of 1 food


 - Camera Operations

   Arrow Up      : move forward
   Arrow Down    : move backward
   Arrow Left    : strafe left
   Arrow Right   : strafe right
   Home          : move up
   End           : move down
   NumKey 2      : look up
   NumKey 8      : look down
   NumKey 4      : look left
   NumKey 6      : look right


TERMINOLOGY

 - Adam
      : new (100% random) critter

 - Adam Distance (ad)
      : mutations since adam



